About Pneumaengine

  • Who we are
  • Trusted platforms
  • Teams
  • Chat
  • Sentiment Analysis

We're IT professionals with years of experience and a real drive to make esports better. Our platform is all about tracking events, numbers and stats — everything that matters and defines modern esports and its future.

The best streaming platforms from around the world. If it’s reliable and carries esports, we gather and process the data.

Stats and analytics on professional squads from all the relevant games and tournaments. The people that matter now, the ones that made history, and the rising stars of tomorrow.

Our complex Twitch chat tracking technology analyzes the number of new and returning users, viewing times, overlapping game audiences and much more!

page.home.about.text.5

We go beyond simple numbers: our Sentiment Analysis method tracks viewers’ emotional reactions by analyzing chat messages!
